---
title: "cx memory context — Composition Pipeline"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as 🤖 Agent
    participant CX as ⚙️ cx binary
    participant IDX as 📇 .index.db (FTS5)
    participant Files as 📁 .cx/ markdown files
    participant Local as 💾 ~/.cx/memory.db

    Agent->>CX: cx memory context

    Note over CX: Check if .index.db needs rebuild
    CX->>Files: Compare file mtimes vs last_indexed_at
    
    alt Files changed since last index
        CX->>Files: Read all .md files in observations/, decisions/, sessions/
        CX->>IDX: Parse frontmatter + content → rebuild FTS5 index
    end

    Note over CX: 1. LATEST SESSION (~150 tokens)
    CX->>IDX: SELECT * FROM indexed_entities<br/>WHERE entity_type='session'<br/>AND author='angel'<br/>ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1
    IDX-->>CX: Session: BLE pairing state machine

    Note over CX: 2. ACTIVE DECISIONS (~100 tokens)
    CX->>IDX: SELECT * FROM indexed_entities<br/>WHERE entity_type='decision'<br/>AND status='active'<br/>ranked by relevance to cwd
    IDX-->>CX: Top 3 decisions (title + outcome only)

    Note over CX: 3. RECENT OBSERVATIONS (~150 tokens)
    CX->>IDX: SELECT * FROM indexed_entities<br/>WHERE entity_type='observation'<br/>AND created_at > 7 days ago<br/>ranked by relevance > recency
    IDX-->>CX: Top 5 observations (title + one-line)

    Note over CX: 4. PERSONAL NOTES (~100 tokens)
    CX->>Local: FTS5 search: current project name<br/>+ current directory keywords
    Local-->>CX: Top 3 personal notes

    Note over CX: Compose output (~500 tokens total)
    CX-->>Agent: Formatted context:<br/>Session Recovery + Active Decisions +<br/>Recent Observations + Personal Notes
